snippet.textDisplay:
I think Kourtney should take time off. She hasn't been happy doing the show in some time. I think she wants the lifestyle without working. Unfortunately that isn't a reality. But, obviously the show isn't helping her mental health, which is the most important thing. What I don't see in the comments is acknowledgement that yes, even though Kourtney is going through something, her response of physically lashing out at Kim wasn't warranted from Kim's comment. Kim's comment was annoying, but Kourtney's reaction was not appropriate or equal to the comment. Resorting to physical violence is just not okay.


I think it's also important to understand both sides. Khloe and Kim are both (and have been) picking up Kourtney's slack on the show, while getting paid the same. That isn't right. They're frustrated because Kourtney continually doesn't pull her weight at their expense. Kourtney is annoyed because she's sick of feeling like she's living her life in a way that she doesn't want to be. I get it. That would be so grating to live like that.
